    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Everything runs smoothly, it looks great parked in the driveway, and it's just a dependable, fun car all around. If you're looking for something reliable that still feels fresh, you're going to love this one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
