    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This well-cared-for vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and practicality for its next owner. The exterior paint still holds a deep, attractive luster, showing only the expected minor surface marks and small stone chips consistent with careful road use. Step inside to a clean, smoke-free interior where the upholstery remains firm and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the navigation system\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; the engine idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. We have recently performed a comprehensive fluid service and a brake pad replacement to ensure it is turn-key ready. Included with the sale are the original owner\u2019s manuals, two sets of keys, and a folder of recent maintenance receipts. This is a solid, honest car that has been maintained with an eye for detail.",
      "price": 34800.0,
