    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes both performance and reliability. It remains in commendable condition, having undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure all mechanical systems operate with precision. With its refined interior and well-preserved exterior, this offering represents an exceptional investment in long-term driving satisfaction.",
      "price": 34900.0,
