    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It has been so reliable for me and is still looking sharp and running great! It\u2019s in that sweet spot where it's been well-loved but still has so much life left to give. It\u2019s super clean and ready for your next road trip. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how smoothly it handles. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 33800.0,
