      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry remains precise with recently refreshed control arm bushings and dampers. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car with high mechanical integrity.",
